content: Yes, I am familiar with Snarky Puppy's music. They are a talented group of musicians who have created a unique sound by combining different genres of music such as jazz, funk, and rock. Snarky Puppy has won several Grammy Awards and has a massive fan following for their innovative and soulful music. Their performances are always energetic, and their improvisational skills are impressive. If you like funky jazz fusion, you must check out other fusion jazz artists like Herbie Hancock, Chick Corea, and Weather Report.
